<div class="header">
  <h2>학생 CSV 일괄 등록</h2>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    다음 컬럼이 포함된 CSV 파일을 업로드하세요:
    <code>name, email, password, school_id, class_id, student_code</code>
  </p>

  <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <strong>CSV 파일 양식 예시:</strong>
    <pre style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">name,email,password,school_id,class_id,student_code
홍길동,hong@example.com,password123,1,1,2024001
김철수,kim@example.com,password123,1,1,2024002</pre>
  </div>

  <%= form_with url: import_school_manager_students_path, method: :post, multipart: true, local: true do |f| %>
    <div class="form-group">
      <%= f.label :file, "CSV 파일" %>
      <%= f.file_field :file, accept: ".csv" %>
    </div>

    <div class="actions">
      <%= f.submit "업로드", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      <%= link_to "취소", school_manager_students_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
